# 📊 Power BI Project: Zepto Sales Dashboard

## 🎯 Project Objective
Analyze Zepto's sales data to derive actionable business insights on revenue, customer behavior, product performance, and profitability.

## 📂 Dataset Overview
- **Source**: Zepto (Sample Sales Dataset)
- **Key Columns**:
  - Order ID
  - Customer Name
  - Product Category
  - Sales Amount
  - Order Date
  - Location / Region
  - Quantity Sold
  - Profit Margin

## 🔎 Key Insights
- Top-performing product categories identified.
- Monthly sales trend analysis with seasonality detection.
- Regional sales performance visualized.
- Customer segments contributing major revenue.
- Profitability trends across products.

## 🛠 Tools & Techniques
- **Power Query**: Data cleaning, transformation, and preparation.
- **DAX**: KPIs, calculated measures, time intelligence.
- **Visualizations**: Bar Charts, Pie Charts, Line Charts, Maps, KPI Cards, Interactive Slicers.


## 📁 Files Included
- Zepto_Project.pbix (Power BI file)
- Dashboard_Screenshots (Folder)


